data.description:
COME BUY THIS DREAM HOME! This stunning home features 3 spacious bedrooms, each adorned with gorgeous hardwood floors, providing both elegance and durability.  Tons of updates throughout, new vanities in all 3 bathrooms, new flooring in kitchen, baths, and entry from garage.   The driveway has a new layer of asphalt to welcome your vehicles into the oversized 2-car garage.   There’s a half-bath in the garage and access door to the backyard. Roof and Hot Water Tank were replaced 2 years ago. 

The lower level could be used as a non-conforming bedroom, theater, or home office - the possibilities are endless! 

You will love the oversized deck, ready for the installation of a new Jacuzzi Hot Tub.

American Home Shield Warranty is currently in place through August 2024, will be transferrable to buyer at closing. It has a $100 Service Fee.

Note: X Flood Zone, minimal flood hazard. 

The yard is perfect for family events, and your furry loves will enjoy too! 

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely home yours - schedule a showing today!
